name: Begin Landing Your Troops
Lore: 'Once begun, the occupation of Naboo was swift, and devastatingly effective.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your unique (•) Republicans are forfeit +2 and immune to Goo Nee Tay. Unless Imperial Arrest Order on table, once during your deploy phase, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
